    public class EditOrDelete
extends MainActivity
    Once a record is created, the user can click on that record to access this screen. Here the user can either edit or delete the data. if (user clicks on list view object) user can edit: if (user clicks delete): record is deleted-count is changed This class is very similar to CreateActivity.java and uses the same techniques to fill in user data
    See Also:
